'''Shadow Droids''' is an article written by [[Morrie Mullins (real person)|Morrie Mullins]] as a tie in to the [[Living Force (roleplaying campaign)|Living Force]] campaign. It was published on the [[Wizards of the Coast]] website on [[October 10]] [[2002]] and took the form of recording made by an agent for the [[Office of Peace and Security]] of a coversation with some bar patrons with regard to droid pilots in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]].

